  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-xs-12 text-center">
        <p class="text-muted">Thank you for taking the time to combat climate change denial in our own special way!</p>
        <p class="text-muted">Special thanks to our sources:</p>
        <ul class="footer-list">
          <li><a href="http://www.barackobama.com/#get-the-latest">Organize for Action</a></li>
          <li><a href="http://sunlightfoundation.com/">Sunlight Foundation</a></li>
          <li><a href="https://www.opensecrets.org/">Open Secrets</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

